T1  - American Association of Clinical Endocrinology Clinical Practice Guideline: Developing a Diabetes Mellitus Comprehensive Care Plan-2022 Update
A1  - Blonde L.
A1  - Umpierrez G.E.
A1  - Reddy S.S.
A1  - McGill J.B.
A1  - Berga S.L.
A1  - Bush M.
A1  - Chandrasekaran S.
A1  - DeFronzo R.A.
A1  - Einhorn D.
A1  - Galindo R.J.
