T1  - Dunnigan lipodystrophy syndrome: French National Diagnosis and Care Protocol (PNDS; Protocole National de Diagnostic et de Soins)
A1  - Mosbah H.
A1  - Donadille B.
A1  - Vatier C.
A1  - Janmaat S.
A1  - Atlan M.
A1  - Badens C.
A1  - Barat P.
